templateVersions.content:
Summarize all interactions with this person account. Includes a list of previous items discussed and includes a list of outstanding action items. Contacts Name: {!$Input:Account.PersonContact.Name}
Use this information as background: {!$Flow:gps_Get_Interaction_Summary_for_Account.Prompt}
Format the output in the following way: Overview: 2-3 sentence overview summarize previous interactions List of activities: Bulleted list of past activities in chronological order. Each bullet should be limited to 1 sentence. List of action items: Bulleted list of action items. Each bullet should be 1 sentence or sentence fragment Use Rich Text Markup in generated text.
